<div class="title">Friday Night Phenethylamines</div>
<div class="substance">25I-NBOMe</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=twilly&Exact=1">twilly</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; twilly. "Friday Night Phenethylamines: An Experience with 25I-NBOMe (exp99081)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 28, 2013. erowid.org/exp/99081</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

